title: Sumski Kuhar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Raw, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Croatian
description: Veggie restaurant in the city center. Offers an assortment soups and dishes made of organic vegetables, grains, herbs. Juices, smoothies, tea, and desserts are available, as are raw food. 3 menus daily: raw food, fast food, daily menu. Has hemp food and beverages. Nature ambiance. Closed July-August months.
